divs: Sighting Detailsi waled out side to...piss.... i looked up in the sky...and saw 3 sets of 2 lights small, rectangular, evenly spaced, heading south to north... they all curved east in a line and i lost sight... no sound at all... i have seen planes, large and small, helicopters and search lights.... this was none of the above... i lost sight as they moved too far to see... 5 seconds max
Summary: 3 sets of 2 lights moving very fast, turned east and lined up, then lost sight...no sound
